product_name: Zefal Mini EZ Push CO2 Tire Inflator - 2013 Overstock
long_description: The Zefal Mini EZ Push CO2 Tire Inflator is easy to use so you'll be ready to ride in seconds. Included 16g cartridge fills one 27 in. road tire to 130 psi or one 26 in. mountain bike tire to 40 psi in seconds. Works with 12g, 16g and 25g threaded cartridges, additional cartridges not included. Overstock.
